<br>
Savant Cap<br>
Foreman's Tunic<br>
Cracked Darkwood Shield or Charred Guardian Shield (better)<br>
Combine Scimitar<br>
+2 wis rings (gold jasper?)<br>
Leather legs til you get Gatorscale<br>
Splitpaw Gloves, Belt, Mask<br>
Kobold Hide Boots<br>
<br>
I think that stuff is pretty much attainable around lvl 20 if you're set on not twinking at all. If you want to twink a little, get...<br>
<br>
Gatorscale Leggings<br>
Chipped Bone Bracelets<br>
+3 wis earrings<br>
Silver Ruby Veil<br>
Azure Sleeves or Ulthork Hide or Giant Scalemail Sleeves<br>
Runed Falchion<br>
<br>
Anyway, hope that helps some, good luck :)<br>
